metadata.name: You Are-VIP Edition #1/7
metadata.description:
You Are is a practice of manifestation. Love is universal, but at the time of writing this I was specifically preparing myself for the person I wanted to love forever. I laid in bed and allowed the words to flow. Then, something beautiful was birthed. And so it is.

This project is special to me because it's centered around Independence-and the power to choose, create, and cultivate my own path.

Holders Will Receive:

* A digital ticket to the first ever Jazii live concert, featuring both NFT music and unreleased tracks as well. This experience will offer the option for holders to attend in person or via live streaming on 03.20.2022  
* Cover art created by Izz (@Izzakko)  
* Downloadable mp3 of “You Are”  
* Voting rights to select the first song to be released from my upcoming live visual project.  
* Jazii POAP
